This repository contains modifications to the AMD FidelityFX(TM) SDK 2.2 samples
("Redstone") for automated command-line benchmarking. It does NOT include the
FidelityFX SDK itself — only the modified source and config files (src/) and an
equivalent unified diff (patches/). Obtain the base source separately:

    FidelityFX-Samples-v2.2.0-source.zip  (AMD GPUOpen / GitHub release v2.2.0)

