are under the MIT License; the proprietary FidelityFX effect/ML components and SDK
core are under a binary-redistribution-only, no-reverse-engineering license. The
modifications in this repository are MIT licensed (see LICENSE), consistent with the
MIT tier of the files they modify. Full breakdown and all license texts are in
licenses/. FidelityFX is a trademark of Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.

Modified files (see patches/redstone-benchmark.patch for the exact changes):
  Kits/Cauldron2/dx12/framework/core/framework.cpp        (Display Avg FPS in CSV/JSON; timestamped output; -vsync / -nolimit benchmark-integrity flags)
  Kits/Cauldron2/dx12/framework/core/framework.h          (present-count members; DisableFPSLimit config field)
  Kits/Cauldron2/dx12/rendermodules/skydome/skydomerendermodule.cpp   (skydome CLI overrides)
  Samples/Upscalers/FidelityFX_FSR/dx12/fsrapirendermodule.cpp        (FSR + FG CLI knobs)
  Samples/Denoisers/FidelityFX_Denoiser/dx12/denoiserrendermodule.cpp (Ray Regen CLI knobs)
  Samples/Denoisers/FidelityFX_Denoiser/dx12/fsrapirendermodule.cpp   (scale preset CLI)
  Samples/RadianceCaches/FidelityFX_NRC/dx12/D3DPipeline.cpp          (NRC benchmark + CLI knobs)
  Samples/RadianceCaches/FidelityFX_NRC/dx12/RenderManager.cpp        (NRC -forcewmma)
  Samples/RadianceCaches/FidelityFX_NRC/dx12/Win32.cpp                (NRC -resolution)
  Kits/Cauldron2/dx12/framework/config/cauldronconfig.json            (default resolution 1920x1080)
  Samples/RadianceCaches/FidelityFX_NRC/dx12/config.json             (default resolution 1920x1080)
